feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 25, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104evh1701459402966.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/evh1701459402966.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/evh1701459402966.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"evh1701459402966\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">UX Widget Class APIs allow users to build a consistent UX/UI. It opens up parts of\n\t\tUniface needed to efficiently interact with the core of Uniface, while providing proper\n\t\tisolation of concerns keeping the development of custom constructs easy and\n\t\tmaintainable.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">UX Widget Class APIs support field-level, entity-level (collection and occurrence), and\n\t\t\tcomponent-level widgets. The sub-sections showcase the list of currently supported\n\t\t\tAPIs.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For details on UX Widget States and API Functions, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qgj1701437193772.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgj1701437193772.html\" title=\"The following sections explain various UX widget states and it's API functions.\">UX Widget States and API Functions</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"evh1701459402966__section_xr4_p4k_mhc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1036144e62\">API Function Applicability Matrix</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This section provides a quick reference for UX Widget Class API functions and their\n\t\t\t\tapplicability across different widget types.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following table shows which API functions are available for each widget type:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"7\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/><col style=\"width:14.285714285714285%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__1\">API Function</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__2\">Field</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__3\">Collection</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__4\">Occurrence</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__5\">Component</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__6\">Phase</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__7\">Notes</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">processLayout()</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__2\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ds4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__3\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_es4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__4\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_fs4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__5\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_gs4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__6\">Static</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__7\">Provides initial HTML layout</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">constructor()</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__2\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_is4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__3\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_js4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__4\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ks4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__5\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ls4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__6\">Creation</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__7\">Creates widget instance</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">onConnect()</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__2\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ns4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__3\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_os4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__4\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ps4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__5\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_qs4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__6\">Connection</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__7\">Connects widget to DOM</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__1\"><strong class=\"ph b\">mapTrigger()</strong></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__2\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ss4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__3\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_ts4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__4\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_us4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__5\"><img alt=\"function is called for this widget type\" class=\"image\" id=\"evh1701459402966__image_vs4_p4k_mhc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/Function_Is_called_for_this_widget_type.png?_LANG=enus\"/></td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__6\">Connection</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"evh1701459402966__table_yr4_p4k_mhc__entry__7\">Maps triggers to DOM events</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry 